24 July
en Jan Kent & comp
In answer to yours of 24 & 28 past, & 5 cur the ostendish convoy is
arrived, bat I can not butt wh vere mnst wonder that you have not
performed my orders you drive the trade to your minde, the 19 jny last
have rexpressed to you how manney fine ones I ordered, & of all them there is
butt b forwarded, if you wil peruse my orders for spanish cloathes, you will
finde, that you had to provide about 40 pieces & time thereunden
17 superfine & of all them I have butt 6 & 6 others, so that there wants
28p. to compleate my demant, & now the convoy is arrived, & god knowes
when to have them, & in the meane while, I have rengaged to delivre them
here: what don now, before they bee here the mode may bee
changed: I have no small peason to compleane, of this your negligence
others serve mee exaeter, in spanish cloathes then you, butt I doubt you
have to much to dos, now seeing you wayt forther order, for what
I will have that shall beethen onley for one pack of spanish cloathes
according to the inclosed instruction & no more as to my goods from
eisier amsterdam or Rottet
the north I exspect them p the first convoy d rest

In answer to yours of 27 may last in thomas is well arived att
bridges with your tobacco, & hope to seeimg them here within
weeks whenly shall endeavour to sell them as soone as posible, & act
there in, as for my selfs yett pray lett mee know, if p may sel them
att prile courant, & by the candele, in case, I can not sell to content,
mich
outp ofhand, for here is move tobacco, brought in from holland,
& the countryes full of armyes, yett the demand p consomption
is not accordingley in'exspectation of your answer remaine

25 July
Brussel procureur de hulder
In antwoort aenden ue van 21 deser, betrouwe ende verwachte door ue goede
vigilantie, dat den heer raedt de man rapporteur sal wesen hij is venoude
laecke sonderlingh niet geinformeert maer alsoo het is een cas van rechte, en van
onse costumen, en dat de voors heer daer in volcommentlijck is gevaceert ende
diergelycke saecken hem vl liyck wel syn voorgevallen, soo mach ue
dat pretent wel gebruycken, al oft hy daer van geinformeert was om hem alsoo
voor rapporteur te becommen ick was eerst geraden gewoorden den h
des champs te versoecken, om dat hj hier op de selve maniere eenen pandt heeft
geabandoneert voorderente, doch ick woorde geinformeert dat din de man
expedienten is, behalven dat ick bij den selven particuliere recommandatie sal
becommen tot d'expeditie t'welck het eenigh is wat wij noodich hebben want
aen ons recht geen achter dencken woort gemaeck wat passeert is mij aengenaem
te vennemen ende blijve
